    dc:description "Figure 1. Eumerus druk Smit, sp. nov., male holotype A lateral view B metaleg, lateral view C abdomen, lateral view D dorsal view E head, frontal view. Eumerus druk Smit, sp. nov., female paratype F lateral view." ;
